column12:
What's New?
In an attempt to ever improve my scoring process, as well as provide more insight in a much more readable fashion, I've introduced a new 'Manufacturer Statistics' box as well as two tabs 'Hard' and 'Soft' Totals. The manufacturer stats box, above, ranks the average of all tested switches from that brand compared to other brands. While this isn't the best metric currently, I'll be adding more to brands with few entries such as Outemu and Cherry over time. As well, I've now divided my 5 categories into 'Hard' performance based metric and 'Soft' context based metric rankings as well in order to readers to better ascertain these rankings without the influence of the others, even though they combined tell the entire 'Overall' ranking of a switch.
